柯克·哈米特（Kirk Hammett）有767张新的即将来临的金属专辑，他说他们的声音可以“再次回到90年代” https://www.nme.com/news/music/kirk-hammett-has-767-new-riffs-for-next-metallica-album-says-their-sound-could-go-back-to-the-90s-again-3848800?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=kirk-hammett-has-767-new-riffs-for-next-metallica-album-says-their-sound-could-go-back-to-the-90s-againMax Pilley Mon, 24 Mar 2025 16:10:49 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3848800 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他说他认为乐队不会“至少又一年”开始录制唱片，但是</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kirk-hammett-has-767-new-riffs-for-next-metallica-album-says-their-sound-could-go-back-to-the-90s-again-3848800">柯克·哈米特（Kirk Hammett）邮报有767张新的即将来临专辑，他说他们的声音可以“回到90年代再次回到90年代”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kirk_hammett_metallica-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>柯克·哈米特（Kirk Hammett）透露，他在下一张<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a>专辑中拥有767个新的即兴演奏，并认为唱片可能会看到他们“再次回到90年代”。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1053" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/metallica-72-seasons-review-3429742"><b>Metallica  - &#39;72季节&#39;评论：金属大师们不懈地回报</b></a></li></ul><p>《金属图标》的首席吉他手在接受<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/kirk-hammett-book-solo-album-metallica-podcast-interview-1235301767/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>滚石乐队</i></a>的新采访中，对乐队的随访<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/metallica-72-seasons-review-3429742">时间</a>开放，这表明他们不会开始在下一张专辑“至少又一年”上工作。</p><p>他说：“我有767张新专辑的新专辑。” “这也是一场噩梦，正在经历这些事情。我是负责所有这些事情的人，我做不到……。我预见到我们至少要又开始了下一张专辑，因为我们仍在完成<i>72个季节的</i>巡回演出。”</p><p> “一旦我们完全完成了这一点，然后去了亚洲，澳大利亚和新西兰等所有外围的地方，我认为我们会休息一下，而不是太多，然后我们就会重新融入其中。” </p><figure id="attachment_3828590" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828590" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828590" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/metallica@2000x1270.jpg" alt="metallica" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/metallica@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/metallica@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/metallica@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/metallica@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/metallica@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/metallica@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828590" class="wp-caption-text"> Metallica表演现场表演。学分：哈维尔·布拉加多/雷德尔</figcaption></figure><p>“ M72 World Tour”于2023年4月开始，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/metallica-add-new-us-dates-to-m72-world-tour-with-support-from-limp-bizkit-and-pantera-3795180">于4月在纽约锡拉丘兹重新开始</a>。预定日期是11月19日在新西兰奥克兰。</p><p>哈米特还讨论了新唱片的潜在声音。 “谁知道？我们可能只是说，&#39;好吧，让我们再次回到九十年代&#39;。这不是一个坏主意！我们还没有互相说。这很有趣。因为当“负载<i>”</i>和“重新加载<i>”</i>出来时，有很多强烈反对。但是，如今，我遇到了粉丝，他们喜欢那个时代，他们喜欢那个时代。”</p><p> “We play &#39;Fuel&#39; and people go nuts. We play &#39;Until It Sleeps&#39; and people know every word. It&#39;s kind of like how when I was a teenager, I listened to all the Zeppelin albums except &#39;Zeppelin III&#39; because it was more acoustic and I just wanted the high-energy aggressive stuff. But over time I really came to embrace &#39;Zeppelin III&#39; and how wonderful it is.”</p><p>这位吉他手说，在62岁的时候，他仍然像以往一样被射击。他说：“我觉得我还在攀登山顶。” “尚未到达山顶。还没有到达金字塔的顶峰。仍然上升，伙计。我仍然觉得自己正在进步，而且我仍然有很多创造性的动力和精力。”</p><p>在反思Metallica的未来时，他补充说：“很多都与个人健康有关。我不会觉得自己正在结束。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/metallicas-kirk-hammett-to-release-new-book-exploring-extraordinary-guitar-collection-and-life-in-music-3848108">哈米特（Hammett）发行了一本新的咖啡桌书， <i>《收藏：柯克·哈米特》（Kirk Hammett）</i></a> ，该书将探索他的吉他收藏和音乐生活，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/metallicas-kirk-hammett-to-release-new-book-exploring-extraordinary-guitar-collection-and-life-in-music-3848108">Metallica宣布了“沉浸式”新的VR电影音乐会的详细信息</a>，他们与Apple Vision Pro合作。</p><p> Metallica还参加了7月在伯明翰市维拉公园（Villa Park）的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-final-show-birmingham-july-2025-metalla-slayer-pantera-line-up-tickets-3835042">最后一个有史以来的Black Sabbath表演的堆积阵容</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kirk-hammett-has-767-new-riffs-for-next-metallica-album-says-their-sound-could-go-back-to-the-90s-again-3848800">柯克·哈米特（Kirk Hammett）邮报有767张新的即将来临专辑，他说他们的声音可以“回到90年代再次回到90年代”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
